<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/20929126">拖延现象（拖延症）的成因有哪些？如何应对？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="552149" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"></div>


</div>
